FAQs
Clinical study
Published in the journal Pediatria Rural y Extrahospitalaria.
“Cry Translator is an effective translator for baby crying, helping parents/baby care-givers to pay early and effective attention which can soothe a baby crying.”
Why is my baby crying?
In less than five seconds an output is given with the translation of the baby's crying, relating to one of a number of states: hunger, sleep, discomfort, stress or simply bored.
